            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "79:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ﴾: فَعَاقَبَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ﴾: عَذابَ الآخِرَةِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ﴾: وَعَذابَ الدُّنيا.</h2>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "79:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَعِبۡرَةٗ﴾: لَمَوْعِظَةً.</h2>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "79:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ﴾: أبَعْثُكُم-أيُّها الناسُ- بَعْدَ الموتِ أَشَدُّ في تَقْدِيرِكُم أم خَلْقُ السَّماءِ؟</p>\n<h2>﴿بَنَىٰهَا﴾: خَلَقَها.</h2>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "79:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا﴾: رَفَعَها فَوقَكُم كالبِناءِ فَأَعلى سَقْفَها في الهوَاءِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿فَسَوَّىٰهَا﴾: فعَدَّلَ أَجْزَاءَها بإتْقان.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "79:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا﴾: وَأَظْلَمَ لَيْلَها.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا﴾: وَأَبْرَزَ نَهارَها.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "79:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ﴾: بَعْدَ خَلْقِ السَّماءِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿دَحَىٰهَآ﴾: بَسَطَها وَأَوْدَعَ فِيها منافِعَها.</h2>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "79:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا﴾: وَأَنبَتَ فِيها ما يُرعَى مِنَ النباتاتِ.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "79:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَرۡسَىٰهَا﴾: أَثْبتَهَا في الأرضِ.</h2>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "79:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ﴾: مَنفَعَةً لَكُم.</h2>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "79:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ﴾: القِيامَةُ الكُبْرَى والشِّدَّةُ العُظْمَى وهي النَّفْخَةُ الثَّانِيةُ.</p>"
        },
